(143, 26, '_panels_data_preview', 'a:3:{s:7:"widgets";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:6:"filter";s:1:"1";s:4:"text";s:1266:"<div class="blog-left-left wow fadeInUp animated animated" data-wow-delay=".5s"><h2>Global Presence</h2></div><div class="blog-left-right wow fadeInUp animated animated" data-wow-delay=".5s"><p>Goldmoore Pharma is 100% export oriented company with diverse products portfolio which includes drugs that cater to nutrition, infectious diseases, gastro-enteritis, pain management, cardiovascular ailment, central nervous system related ailments and various Herbal and Ayurvedic products.</p><p>Goldmoore Pharma has strong presence in West African and East African region and exporting to 8 countries. With more than 50 products already registered and 45 products in process. Goldmoore Pharma finest quality finished formulations will reach to more and more masses.</p><p>Goldmoore Pharma has already started registration process of 11 products with Latin American countries and our immediate goal is to spread our wings to 10 more countries in Latin America and South East Asia.</p><p>Our global presence is built on a strong foundation of mutual respect : Respect for cultural and social diversity and respect for globally shared values.</p><p>Goldmoore Pharma promises for keeping pace with International Standards to penetrate further into the Global field.</p></div>";s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";s:11:"panels_info";a:7:{s:5:"class";s:31:"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget";s:3:"raw";b:0;s:4:"grid";i:0;s:4:"cell";i:0;s:2:"id";i:0;s:9:"widget_id";s:36:"7e48222e-a9e8-4e77-b3c1-eabf6513f4d4";s:5:"style";a:0:{}}}}s:5:"grids";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:"cells";i:1;s:5:"style";a:0:{}}}s:10:"grid_cells";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"grid";i:0;s:6:"weight";i:1;}}}'),
