(19, 1, '2017-02-18 15:53:23', '2017-02-18 15:53:23', '<p>In December 2005 the company established its manufacturing arm, Pharmaceuticals Limited, as a direct response to the economic initiatives of the Federal Government at ensuring that the private sector takes the driving seat of the national development process, also as the administration drive in encouraging local drug manufacturing in the country</p>\r\n<p>Goldmoore Pharmaceuticals state of the art factory has Good Manufacturing Practices Certification (GMP) approved by NAFDAC and has over 250 qualified and highly skilled personnel made up of foreign Nationals and Nigerians overseeing the production activities of the company.</p>\r\n<p>We have well over 150 products in antimalarial, multivitamin, anti-hypertensive, antipsychotic, anaesthetics, anti-diabetics, anti-inffectives, analgesics, anti-fungi, anti-ulcer etc.</p>\r\n<p>Our group has vast experience in the production, marketing and distribution of high quality pharmaceutical drugs. We possess premium track record of handling successful briefs even related briefs such as partnering with various organizations in delivering qualitative health care to their target.</p>\r\n<p>Our products are of the high standard.We have well over 150 products in antimalarial, multivitamin, anti-hypertensive, antipsychotic, anaesthetics, antidiabetics, anti-effectives, analgesics, anti-fungi, anti-ulcer.We have 250 higly qualified and commited team.Engages in community sevices as responsible corporate citizen</p>', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2017-02-18 17:03:56', '2017-02-18 17:03:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=19', 0, 'page', '', 0),
